  <h1>About Steer Clear</h1>

  <span class="content">Steer Clear is a safe-ride program for the College of William and Mary students that provides a reliable, secure
    and <b>free</b> means of travel for students on weekend nights when school is in session. </span>
  <span class="content">The organization aims to reduce risky behavior, namely driving under the influence and traveling unescorted during late hours. </span>

